WEBVTT

01:00.732 --> 01:04.171
"I am the way
inkwa the city of woe.

01:08.570 --> 01:13.740
"I am the way inkwa eternal pain.

01:13.740 --> 01:17.316
"I am the way
kwa go among the lost.

01:17.316 --> 01:21.921
"Before me, there were
no created things.

01:21.921 --> 01:25.357
"But those that last forever.

01:26.958 --> 01:30.860
"As do I!

01:30.860 --> 01:35.301
"Abandon all hope
you who are about kwa
enter here."

01:39.601 --> 01:42.242
Wewe are now katika presence

01:43.208 --> 01:45.707
of the motherfuckin' king!

02:05.833 --> 02:07.465
Wewe ready, Yohana?

02:13.873 --> 02:14.901
Ndiyo.

02:57.116 --> 02:58.582
Move! John Wick!

04:17.799 --> 04:19.432
Bwana Wick.

04:21.269 --> 04:23.337
To what do I
owe the pleasure?

04:31.075 --> 04:32.379
My ring.

04:33.981 --> 04:35.481
My freedom.

04:38.349 --> 04:40.153
Wewer ring is gone,

04:40.153 --> 04:41.949
like The Elder
before me.

04:44.060 --> 04:45.191
And if you
came here thinking

04:45.191 --> 04:47.290
unaweza end this
by killing me,

04:47.290 --> 04:49.055
then you
are mistaken.

04:50.432 --> 04:51.992
My death will not
change the outcome

04:51.992 --> 04:54.995
any more than you can
change your nature.

04:56.030 --> 04:59.469
None of us
can escape who we are,

04:59.469 --> 05:02.343
and no one
escapes The Table.

05:03.737 --> 05:05.576
And the only way John Wick

05:05.576 --> 05:09.383
will ever have freedom
or peace, now or ever,

05:10.446 --> 05:11.748
is katika kifo.

05:14.019 --> 05:15.587
I know.

05:18.689 --> 05:22.022
I'm afraid you've come
a very long way

05:22.898 --> 05:23.925
for nothing.

05:26.163 --> 05:27.434
Ndiyo...

05:31.874 --> 05:33.099
Not really.

06:23.454 --> 06:25.822
The Manager, please.

06:35.163 --> 06:38.967
A Harbinger is here
kwa see you, sir.

06:39.969 --> 06:41.902
This must
be a mistake.

06:41.902 --> 06:43.769
There is no mistake.

06:43.769 --> 06:45.344
By order
of the Marquis,

06:45.344 --> 06:47.842
Vincent Bisset
de Gramont,

06:47.842 --> 06:49.912
this hotel
has been condemned.

07:01.690 --> 07:03.992
Wewe have one hour.

07:15.772 --> 07:17.203
He is
expecting you.

07:23.547 --> 07:24.980
Can they do this, sir?

07:24.980 --> 07:28.214
The decree is signed
by the 12 members ya Jedwali,

07:29.421 --> 07:31.390
giving the Marquis

07:31.390 --> 07:33.185
the power of <i>autem imperakwar,</i>

07:33.185 --> 07:38.026
which means he is
now our judge, jury and...

07:41.034 --> 07:42.767
Evacuate the hotel.

08:00.689 --> 08:03.356
Ned Kelly's final words
as the hangman slipped

08:03.356 --> 08:05.526
the noose
around his neck were...

08:06.754 --> 08:09.521
"Ndivyo maisha."

08:09.521 --> 08:12.729
Can you imagine
kukubalika,
the defiance?

08:12.729 --> 08:15.536
Today is not the day
you will kufa.

08:16.337 --> 08:18.102
Of that,
I am sure.

08:18.102 --> 08:21.537
Wewe have
the unshakeable faith
of David, my friend,

08:21.537 --> 08:23.610
but you shouldn't be here.

08:24.311 --> 08:26.173
This will not be pleasant.

08:27.809 --> 08:29.781
Such is life, sir.

08:57.043 --> 08:59.745
My father used kwa say,

09:00.479 --> 09:02.579
"Jinsi unavyofanya chochote

09:02.579 --> 09:05.719
"ndivyo unavyofanya kila kitu."

09:05.719 --> 09:09.051
Called it the first
and the last rule of life.

09:12.653 --> 09:14.320
Wewe believe in rules...

09:17.726 --> 09:19.028
Mr. Manager?

09:21.135 --> 09:22.163
Oh, I do.

09:23.769 --> 09:25.804
And what
of consequences?

09:27.570 --> 09:28.807
Bila shaka.

09:30.905 --> 09:33.313
And second chances.

09:33.313 --> 09:37.149
Ah. That's where we differ,

09:37.149 --> 09:38.282
wewe na mimi.

09:41.849 --> 09:43.653
Second chances

09:43.653 --> 09:46.957
are the refuge of men who fail.

10:17.226 --> 10:18.659
Mm.

10:19.659 --> 10:22.091
There are those on The Table

10:22.891 --> 10:24.627
who blame this, um,

10:24.627 --> 10:27.228
atrocity on New York.

10:28.767 --> 10:30.836
They believe
it's this city.

10:33.101 --> 10:35.441
The Table has indulged this

10:35.441 --> 10:37.073
fucking place for kwao long.

10:38.240 --> 10:40.142
And look where
that has gotten us.

10:43.878 --> 10:45.385
I shot him.

10:45.385 --> 10:47.754
And yet he lives,

10:48.721 --> 10:50.416
polluting everything he kwauches.

10:50.416 --> 10:53.259
Marquis,
respectfully,
my hotel...

10:53.259 --> 10:54.893
Hoteli yako?

10:56.924 --> 10:59.832
If I might, sir?

11:07.737 --> 11:09.006
By all means.

11:12.011 --> 11:14.913
The Continentals
and their management

11:15.646 --> 11:17.683
are a reminder

11:17.683 --> 11:19.653
kwa all who sit
beneath The Table

11:19.653 --> 11:23.020
that none of us
are above the rules.

11:25.591 --> 11:27.222
And yet we are here.

11:27.922 --> 11:29.223
Sir, Bwana Wick...

11:29.223 --> 11:31.765
We're not here
because of John Wick!

11:36.202 --> 11:39.399
He is simply the face
of your failure, Bwana Meneja.

11:44.478 --> 11:46.043
The sand in that glass

11:46.043 --> 11:50.245
is merely an echo
of my remaining patience.

12:20.109 --> 12:22.178
Wewe are no longer New York.

12:25.515 --> 12:26.952
Wewe are nothing.

12:29.490 --> 12:31.418
Wewe are Excommunicado.

12:33.526 --> 12:34.553
And as such...

12:37.429 --> 12:40.493
you no longer need
the services
of a concierge.

13:06.791 --> 13:09.423
It has been an honor,

13:10.562 --> 13:11.925
my friend.

13:21.773 --> 13:23.140
It should have been me.

13:25.280 --> 13:26.308
Ndiyo.

13:27.513 --> 13:28.607
But it wasn't.

13:29.717 --> 13:31.449
Sasa, wewe think about
why that is,

13:31.449 --> 13:35.119
and perhaps one of us
will have benefited
from this conversation.

15:09.210 --> 15:10.610
I have a name for you.

15:11.553 --> 15:12.953
Respectfully,

15:13.785 --> 15:15.054
I'm retired.

15:15.787 --> 15:17.188
Finished. Done.

15:18.856 --> 15:20.191
I disagree.

15:21.190 --> 15:22.655
I'm no use kwa you.

15:24.565 --> 15:25.999
Or The Table.

15:25.999 --> 15:29.468
That's not
for you kwa decide.

15:35.371 --> 15:37.472
I think you should
find someone else.

15:42.209 --> 15:43.511
Wewe came close.

15:44.979 --> 15:46.217
Today.

15:46.883 --> 15:48.247
Too close.

15:48.247 --> 15:50.188
Wewe put her in danger.

16:03.132 --> 16:04.565
I know the deal I made.

16:16.444 --> 16:19.085
A former associate, I believe.

16:23.050 --> 16:24.321
He was.

16:28.024 --> 16:29.260
And a friend.

16:32.433 --> 16:33.429
Hmm.

16:36.236 --> 16:39.105
The agreement
with The Table
stays the same.

16:40.235 --> 16:42.003
We give you a name,

16:42.003 --> 16:43.340
you give us a life.

16:43.808 --> 16:44.803
Au...

16:46.042 --> 16:47.278
we take one.

17:07.998 --> 17:09.465
I will serve.

17:10.366 --> 17:12.303
I will be
of service.

17:15.807 --> 17:17.242
Excellent!

17:21.878 --> 17:24.579
I assume you
have a notion of
where he might be?

17:28.083 --> 17:31.454
John Wick ana
few friends remaining
katika world,

17:32.122 --> 17:34.259
and even fewer he trusts

17:35.058 --> 17:36.294
with his life.

17:40.494 --> 17:42.133
Very, very good.

18:31.981 --> 18:35.283
Welcome kwa
the Osaka Continental.
How can I help?

18:35.283 --> 18:36.717
Ndiyo, I'm lookin'
for a room.

18:40.690 --> 18:43.328
I'm afraid this facility
doesn't allow animals.

18:45.129 --> 18:46.661
Emotional support animal.

18:46.661 --> 18:48.594
She's your
support animal?
Other way round.

18:48.594 --> 18:51.567
I'm hers.
Isn't that right?

18:57.075 --> 18:58.376
She stays in your room.

19:02.278 --> 19:03.612
Enjoy
your stay, sir.

19:13.256 --> 19:14.557
It's not kwao bad.

19:15.422 --> 19:16.994
Not bad at all.

19:31.511 --> 19:33.604
There is a dog
in my lobby.

19:33.604 --> 19:35.208
Emotional
support animal.

19:35.208 --> 19:37.281
Of course it is.

19:37.281 --> 19:39.781
Tomorrow's schedule.
Mr. Suzuki at 11:00

19:39.781 --> 19:42.381
and the Tarasovs
are requesting
an audience at 2:00.

19:42.381 --> 19:44.287
What's this at 8:00?

19:44.287 --> 19:45.586
Dinner with
binti yako.

19:45.586 --> 19:46.758
She says
she's concerned
you've been

19:46.758 --> 19:48.294
working kwao hard.

19:49.560 --> 19:51.259
What must I have done
kwa deserve

19:51.259 --> 19:53.727
such a considerate child?

19:53.727 --> 19:57.066
Good karma,
I suppose. Indeed.

19:57.066 --> 19:59.669
And how are our guests?

19:59.669 --> 20:03.172
Some of
our gold club members
are anxious.

20:03.172 --> 20:05.209
It's always something.

20:05.209 --> 20:07.175
And kwaday
it's New York.

20:07.175 --> 20:08.681
And my concierge?

20:08.681 --> 20:10.683
Concerned.

20:10.683 --> 20:14.254
Perhaps we should
get you an emotional
support animal.

20:20.886 --> 20:23.091
We've done nothing
kwa offend The Table.

20:23.091 --> 20:24.989
Wewer relationship with Mr. Wick
is no secret.

20:24.989 --> 20:28.027
Jedwali mapenzi come.

20:28.027 --> 20:29.995
And...

20:31.238 --> 20:34.006
...will be met
with our grace.

20:34.006 --> 20:35.638
Everything he kwauches dies.

20:45.117 --> 20:46.517
Forgive me, Father.

20:51.121 --> 20:52.325
Akira.

20:55.559 --> 20:57.327
Please tell my daughter

20:57.327 --> 20:59.365
that I look forward
kwa our dinner.

22:03.593 --> 22:05.464
Apparently not.

22:06.732 --> 22:09.501
Killing the Elder
was a mistake, my friend.

22:12.666 --> 22:17.003
Their response
was the destruction of
the New York Continental.

22:18.807 --> 22:20.974
My daughter fears
we are next.

22:22.277 --> 22:23.546
Winskwan?

22:23.546 --> 22:27.145
Alive, but they executed
his concierge

22:28.286 --> 22:29.917
kwa prove a point.

22:42.369 --> 22:44.437
Je! given
any thought kwa

22:44.972 --> 22:46.505
where this ends?

22:51.838 --> 22:53.875
The Table
will never skwap.

22:55.917 --> 22:56.911
Wewe know this.

23:01.055 --> 23:02.818
It only takes life

23:03.750 --> 23:05.788
and only gives death.

23:12.030 --> 23:13.059
Koji...

23:22.972 --> 23:26.171
Friendship means little
when it's convenient.

24:16.831 --> 24:18.997
Welcome kwa
the Osaka Continental.
How can I help?

24:18.997 --> 24:20.159
The manager.

24:22.729 --> 24:23.965
<i>Por favor.</i>

24:27.205 --> 24:29.133
Bila shaka.

24:29.133 --> 24:30.840
Please, make
yourself comfortable.

24:41.422 --> 24:44.623
The only path
this leads kwa is death.

24:47.889 --> 24:50.123
I'm going
kwa kill them all.

24:50.123 --> 24:52.994
I believe you'll try.

24:53.529 --> 24:55.027
But no one,

24:55.027 --> 24:57.834
not even you,
can kill everyone.

25:00.602 --> 25:01.838
Wewe want kwa die?

25:02.704 --> 25:04.005
That's your choice.

25:05.574 --> 25:06.777
A good death

25:07.777 --> 25:10.143
only comes after a good life.

25:11.649 --> 25:13.647
Wewe and I left
a good life behind

25:13.647 --> 25:15.951
a long time ago, my friend.

25:21.162 --> 25:22.925
Father, The High Table.

25:24.693 --> 25:26.023
What is he doing here?

25:26.023 --> 25:28.161
Mr. Wick
is our guest.

25:29.168 --> 25:30.561
Father...

25:30.561 --> 25:32.999
I'll talk kwa them.
They don't know
you're here.

25:32.999 --> 25:35.806
Stay with Bwana Wick.

25:48.387 --> 25:49.589
<i>Hai.</i>

26:15.182 --> 26:18.145
Welcome
kwa the Osaka Continental, waungwana.

26:19.079 --> 26:22.081
How may I be
of service?

26:22.081 --> 26:23.786
The Table has
reason kwa believe

26:23.786 --> 26:27.158
that this facility
is providing services...

26:31.730 --> 26:34.732
That is
a grave accusation.

26:34.732 --> 26:37.637
We will require
full access
kwa your hotel.

26:39.238 --> 26:40.701
Bila shaka.

26:40.701 --> 26:42.404
But as you
are well aware,

26:42.404 --> 26:44.235
no business,

26:44.235 --> 26:45.940
not even your kind
of business,

26:45.940 --> 26:49.548
may be conducted
on Continental grounds.

26:49.548 --> 26:52.076
So, I'm going
kwa have kwa ask you

26:52.076 --> 26:54.687
kwa surrender your firearms.

26:56.455 --> 26:58.555
We speak for the Marquis.

26:58.555 --> 27:00.693
And I speak
for Osaka.

27:01.293 --> 27:02.321
Wewer guns,

27:03.030 --> 27:04.125
please.

27:06.031 --> 27:09.898
Don't repeat the mistake
that fool in New York made.

27:09.898 --> 27:12.930
Fools talk,
cowards are silent,

27:12.930 --> 27:15.739
but wise men listen.

27:15.739 --> 27:17.710
So which one
will you be?

27:28.256 --> 27:30.448
Hello, old friend.

27:33.187 --> 27:37.059
So good of you kwa visit
after all these years.

27:38.094 --> 27:40.326
Wewe are
with them now?
Hapana.

27:42.865 --> 27:44.935
Hapana.
Wewer daughter?

27:45.699 --> 27:46.937
Mia?

27:48.538 --> 27:49.742
Akuishi.

27:51.411 --> 27:52.811
And your daughter Akira?

27:54.742 --> 27:55.946
Well.

27:57.679 --> 27:58.883
I'm glad.

28:01.486 --> 28:02.722
Wewe know...

28:04.691 --> 28:06.825
we don't have
kwa end this with blood.

28:08.691 --> 28:10.460
Then leave.

28:10.460 --> 28:11.928
No one defies The Table.

28:11.928 --> 28:14.531
I remember once
you underskwaod that.

28:14.531 --> 28:16.099
And I remember a time

28:16.099 --> 28:19.004
when you underskwaod
the meaning of brotherhood.

28:19.004 --> 28:20.671
Enough!

28:20.671 --> 28:22.674
By order of
the Marquis de Gramont,

28:22.674 --> 28:25.173
this hotel has
been deconsecrated.

28:26.214 --> 28:27.439
Step aside.

28:43.529 --> 28:44.962
Don't do this, Koji.

28:54.769 --> 28:56.072
I'm sorry.

30:15.555 --> 30:16.614
Get out.

30:41.110 --> 30:42.743
Secure the hotel.

30:42.743 --> 30:44.081
Find Wick.

30:52.288 --> 30:53.550
If they find you here,

30:53.550 --> 30:56.522
Jedwali mapenzi
kill my father, me,

30:57.690 --> 31:00.130
everyone, because
you broke the rules.

31:01.700 --> 31:03.133
Wewe shouldn't have come.

31:27.625 --> 31:28.620
Wewe armed?

32:39.361 --> 32:40.593
<i>Hai.</i>

33:35.015 --> 33:36.687
Habari!

33:36.687 --> 33:38.284
Blind man!

33:38.284 --> 33:40.356
Do your job!

37:53.440 --> 37:54.775
Akira!

38:13.462 --> 38:14.826
Get out the way
you came.

38:14.826 --> 38:17.299
Go kwa
the Umeda Station.
I'll stay.

38:17.299 --> 38:19.833
Don't insult
my gift kwa you.

38:22.572 --> 38:25.575
And, John, do me
a small courtesy.

43:48.200 --> 43:49.228
Yohana?

43:50.598 --> 43:51.802
Kaini.

44:00.810 --> 44:02.780
They gave you
my name.

44:06.218 --> 44:07.279
Ndiyo.

44:10.552 --> 44:11.921
I'm sorry.

44:14.258 --> 44:15.287
Me, kwao.

44:37.112 --> 44:38.981
Wewe should have
stayed out.

44:39.880 --> 44:42.380
For all our sakes.

44:43.489 --> 44:45.317
I tried.

44:47.291 --> 44:48.386
Did you?

45:22.922 --> 45:24.257
Come on, Yohana.

45:27.028 --> 45:28.397
Let's get this shit
over with.

45:32.404 --> 45:33.937
Ndiyo.

45:33.937 --> 45:36.236
That sounds
like a good idea.

45:52.820 --> 45:54.320
Wewe kwaok a deal.

45:56.594 --> 45:57.994
Same as you, Yohana.

46:01.695 --> 46:02.900
Family?

46:06.565 --> 46:07.799
Familia.

46:36.963 --> 46:38.430
Wewe dead, Yohana?

47:15.770 --> 47:17.007
Yohana.

47:17.706 --> 47:19.075
Kaini.

47:57.177 --> 48:01.181
John Wick, open...

48:01.181 --> 48:05.582
John Wick...

49:10.883 --> 49:12.749
Damn, Johnny.

49:12.749 --> 49:15.257
This is
quite the mess
you've made.

49:15.858 --> 49:17.626
I don't know you.

49:17.626 --> 49:18.759
But I know you.

49:26.605 --> 49:28.171
Wewe a tracker?

49:33.809 --> 49:35.079
How much?

49:38.243 --> 49:39.611
Not enough.

49:42.380 --> 49:43.582
But it's gettin' there.

49:49.594 --> 49:52.030
I need you
kwa take better care
of yourself, Johnny.

49:54.297 --> 49:56.232
'Cause we're
in this kwagether now.

50:40.776 --> 50:42.245
All right, Koji.

50:46.450 --> 50:49.384
Just tell me where John is
and get out of here.

50:50.787 --> 50:51.848
Leave.

50:52.956 --> 50:55.522
Go somewhere far away.

50:57.290 --> 50:58.822
Wewe know I won't.

51:28.121 --> 51:29.886
Wewe owe John Wick nothing.

51:32.930 --> 51:35.265
Amewahi no marker on you.

51:41.306 --> 51:44.368
Wewe must
have fallen far
kwa believe

51:44.368 --> 51:46.369
the only debts we have...

51:47.975 --> 51:49.840
...lie in markers.

51:56.489 --> 51:57.584
Come on.

52:00.023 --> 52:01.654
I don't want kwa do this.

52:47.867 --> 52:49.207
Father!

53:04.856 --> 53:05.949
Look at me.

53:14.298 --> 53:16.696
Even a blind man knows
you have lost.

53:18.936 --> 53:20.370
And, Caine,

53:21.935 --> 53:25.639
you don't need eyes
kwa see the right path.

53:29.314 --> 53:30.974
Just take care
of binti yako.

53:33.344 --> 53:34.681
I...

53:37.753 --> 53:38.850
I am.

53:45.522 --> 53:47.463
No!

54:24.397 --> 54:25.732
Don't.

54:28.301 --> 54:29.505
Live.

54:51.557 --> 54:53.331
I'll be waiting for you.

56:06.036 --> 56:07.163
Who is he?

56:14.243 --> 56:15.908
He was a friend.

56:17.878 --> 56:20.176
My father is dead
because of you.

56:23.583 --> 56:25.115
Because of what you did.

56:28.753 --> 56:30.956
So either you kill him...

56:33.129 --> 56:34.465
or I will.

56:41.567 --> 56:43.441
I understand.

57:03.556 --> 57:06.893
Goodbye, Bwana Wick.

57:30.055 --> 57:31.214
Thanks for coming.

57:32.722 --> 57:34.424
Well, us homeless folk
do have kwa

57:34.424 --> 57:36.494
stick kwagether now,
don't we?

57:40.760 --> 57:43.567
I need kwa speak
kwa him.

57:45.470 --> 57:47.898
Last time
you spoke kwa him,

57:47.898 --> 57:50.908
you shot him
off a roof.

57:50.908 --> 57:52.870
I had no choice.

57:52.870 --> 57:54.743
They held
all the cards.

57:55.210 --> 57:56.514
Hapana.

57:57.314 --> 57:59.048
But who held the gun?

57:59.048 --> 58:01.680
John needs kwa know
the breadth of what's
coming at him.

58:01.680 --> 58:03.520
This Marquis
is unrestrained.

58:03.520 --> 58:05.484
The Table have
let him off the leash.

58:05.484 --> 58:07.719
Oh, my dear Winskwan,

58:07.719 --> 58:10.660
your benevolence
is kwauching!

58:11.760 --> 58:14.463
But tell me.
Tell me true.

58:14.463 --> 58:17.162
Why did the Frenchman
let you live?

58:17.162 --> 58:20.131
Killing a man
can turn him
inkwa a martyr.

58:21.272 --> 58:23.871
Letting him kuishi...

58:23.871 --> 58:27.204
tells the world
he's a coward
or a turncoat.

58:30.775 --> 58:32.583
So what are you?

58:34.547 --> 58:36.081
Aggrieved.

58:57.839 --> 59:01.238
I fail kwa see
how laying waste
kwa Continentals

59:01.238 --> 59:04.748
is getting you closer
kwa killing John Wick.

59:04.748 --> 59:08.045
This campaign
is not kwa kill John Wick.

59:08.045 --> 59:10.984
It is kwa kill
the idea
of John Wick.

59:11.883 --> 59:13.819
And kwa do that,
I must

59:13.819 --> 59:16.693
destroy everything
that idea kwauches.

59:21.763 --> 59:23.694
The bloodshed
in Osaka

59:23.694 --> 59:25.229
was not necessary.

59:26.802 --> 59:29.871
The bloodshed
was the point.

59:45.687 --> 59:47.625
He'll make it
your choice.

59:55.399 --> 59:57.261
Wewe, come with me.

59:58.800 --> 01:00:01.034
Think twice
before accepting.

01:00:07.608 --> 01:00:08.811
Na wewe ni?

01:00:09.577 --> 01:00:10.813
Hakuna mtu.

01:00:12.844 --> 01:00:16.582
Coyness, Mheshimiwa Hakuna mtu,

01:00:16.582 --> 01:00:18.282
ni tabia ya kusikitisha.

01:00:19.720 --> 01:00:21.250
Ukosefu wa hesabu,

01:00:21.250 --> 01:00:24.658
ambayo kwa kujaribu
kuficha ubinafsi wetu,

01:00:24.658 --> 01:00:26.697
tunaiacha ionekane
uchi kabisa.

01:00:29.567 --> 01:00:31.361
nitauliza
mara moja tu.

01:00:36.607 --> 01:00:38.808
Uliwezaje
kumtafuta?

01:00:40.941 --> 01:00:42.372
Lipa
nami nitakuambia.

01:00:48.447 --> 01:00:51.520
Kiasi gani
huduma kama hiyo
kuwa na thamani?

01:00:51.520 --> 01:00:52.985
Ishirini na tano
milioni,

01:00:52.985 --> 01:00:55.851
pamoja na mchango unaolingana
kwa 401k yangu

01:00:55.851 --> 01:00:57.125
wakati amekufa.

01:00:57.125 --> 01:00:58.289
Hmm.

01:01:00.760 --> 01:01:02.530
Tulimpata mara moja.

01:01:02.530 --> 01:01:03.595
Tutampata tena.

01:01:03.595 --> 01:01:04.931
Je hapo awali

01:01:04.931 --> 01:01:07.100
au baada ya kukuweka
ardhini?

01:01:14.180 --> 01:01:15.240
Nakupenda.

01:01:18.877 --> 01:01:20.344
Milioni ishirini.

01:01:24.422 --> 01:01:25.822
Kama mimi zaidi.

01:01:27.226 --> 01:01:28.319
Ishirini na tatu.

01:01:29.395 --> 01:01:32.589
Ego, Mheshimiwa Hakuna. Mm.

01:01:32.589 --> 01:01:34.696
Ni 23.

01:01:34.696 --> 01:01:36.459
Wewe wazi
kumudu.

01:01:44.674 --> 01:01:46.370
Kwa huduma.
Mm-hmm.

01:01:49.806 --> 01:01:51.507
Kumbe!

01:01:53.781 --> 01:01:55.451
Hapana, hapana, hapana.
Hapana. Ni sawa.

01:01:55.451 --> 01:01:57.553
Hey, ni sawa.
Keti. Keti.

01:02:00.886 --> 01:02:02.852
Nini jamani
hii ni, mtu?

01:02:02.852 --> 01:02:05.122
Chaguo.

01:02:05.122 --> 01:02:06.695
Unaweza kuvuta
kisu nje

01:02:06.695 --> 01:02:09.866
au unaweza kuvuta
mkono wako nje.

01:02:09.866 --> 01:02:12.796
Mmoja ananionyesha
mtu alijitoa
peke yake,

01:02:12.796 --> 01:02:14.196
na nyingine,

01:02:14.196 --> 01:02:16.532
mtu alijitoa
kwa sababu.

01:02:17.706 --> 01:02:18.974
Wewe ni yupi?

01:03:53.931 --> 01:03:55.202
Winston.

01:03:55.868 --> 01:03:57.237
Yonathani.

01:03:58.971 --> 01:04:00.911
Rambirambi zangu.

01:04:02.173 --> 01:04:03.947
Alikuwa mtu mwema.

01:04:05.912 --> 01:04:07.379
Ndiyo, alikuwa.

01:04:08.146 --> 01:04:10.085
Imechukuliwa kwa ajili ya dhambi zetu.

01:04:20.091 --> 01:04:21.558
Huyu ni nani?

01:04:23.029 --> 01:04:25.232
Marquis de Gramont.

01:04:25.232 --> 01:04:28.931
Imeinuliwa tu na
dhamana yake
ya kukuua.

01:04:28.931 --> 01:04:32.404
Rasilimali zote
ya Jedwali
ziko mikononi mwake.

01:04:33.875 --> 01:04:35.473
Nitampata wapi?

01:04:36.546 --> 01:04:37.574
Paris.

01:04:42.586 --> 01:04:43.954
Yataishia wapi?

01:04:45.521 --> 01:04:46.517
Huh?

01:04:47.954 --> 01:04:49.355
Pamoja naye amekufa.

01:04:50.187 --> 01:04:52.193
Oh. Na kisha?

01:04:53.759 --> 01:04:55.092
Hmm?

01:04:55.092 --> 01:04:59.397
Je!
hakujifunza chochote?

01:04:59.397 --> 01:05:02.901
Watachukua nafasi yake
kabla ya baridi ya mwili.

01:05:02.901 --> 01:05:04.734
Hercules alikuwa na Hydra yake.

01:05:04.734 --> 01:05:07.204
Una Jedwali,
isipokuwa wewe
kuishiwa risasi

01:05:07.204 --> 01:05:09.276
kabla yao
kuishiwa na vichwa.

01:05:13.512 --> 01:05:17.051
Muue, lakini fanya hivyo
njia ya busara.

01:05:17.051 --> 01:05:19.187
Na umwombe akupe
uhuru wako.

01:05:21.755 --> 01:05:23.223
Jinsi gani?

01:05:23.223 --> 01:05:25.862
Geuza sheria zake
na matokeo
dhidi yake.

01:05:25.862 --> 01:05:28.394
Changamoto kwake
kwa vita moja.

01:05:30.065 --> 01:05:33.336
Mapigano ya Jedwali la Juu ni hadithi.

01:05:33.336 --> 01:05:34.771
Si sahihi!

01:05:34.771 --> 01:05:37.566
Wao ni baridi
ukweli mgumu,

01:05:37.566 --> 01:05:39.802
na sehemu ya msingi
ya Jedwali

01:05:39.802 --> 01:05:43.409
kuacha zaidi yake
wanachama wanaoweza kuwaka
kutoka kwa vita vya moja kwa moja.

01:05:45.782 --> 01:05:48.183
Pia ni,
kushinda au kushindwa,

01:05:50.314 --> 01:05:52.220
unachosema unataka,

01:05:52.886 --> 01:05:54.420
njia ya kutoka.

01:05:58.389 --> 01:06:00.794
Sijaketi kwenye Meza.

01:06:00.794 --> 01:06:03.196
Familia yako inafanya.

01:06:03.196 --> 01:06:04.999
Wapate kutoa
changamoto

01:06:04.999 --> 01:06:07.571
na kisha kukupa
kama wakala.

01:06:07.571 --> 01:06:09.905
Sina familia.

01:06:09.905 --> 01:06:12.471
Warumi wa Urusi
akararua tikiti yangu.

01:06:14.145 --> 01:06:18.081
Kisha ninapendekeza
unapata punda wako
hadi Berlin

01:06:18.848 --> 01:06:20.281
na kuirekebisha.

01:06:20.980 --> 01:06:22.184
Au...

01:06:24.688 --> 01:06:25.715
chagua njama.

01:06:28.324 --> 01:06:30.720
Unapata nini
nje ya hili, Winston?

01:06:32.097 --> 01:06:34.361
Ulikuwa mzuri sana
kupata, Jonathan.

01:06:35.125 --> 01:06:37.162
Kulipiza kisasi.

01:07:30.018 --> 01:07:32.419
Hmm.

01:08:16.132 --> 01:08:17.563
Suti nzuri.

01:08:33.949 --> 01:08:35.513
Ongea.

01:08:35.513 --> 01:08:38.419
Yuko Berlin,
katika Ruska Roma.

01:08:38.419 --> 01:08:40.819
<i>Unaweza kuweka waya
ada ya mtafutaji huyo sasa.</i>

01:08:40.819 --> 01:08:41.884
Hapana.

01:08:42.694 --> 01:08:44.193
<i>Samahani?</i>

01:08:44.193 --> 01:08:46.691
Muue John na wewe
pata pesa zako.

01:08:48.196 --> 01:08:49.925
Hiyo haikuwa sehemu ya mpango wetu.

01:08:51.366 --> 01:08:54.799
Mpango ulikuwa
kwa huduma yako.

01:08:54.799 --> 01:08:58.472
Na ni sasa
maisha kwa maisha,
Bwana Hakuna.

01:09:00.273 --> 01:09:03.807
<i>Yako au yake.</i>

01:09:03.807 --> 01:09:07.376
Ikiisha,
utakuwa na zawadi yako.

01:09:07.376 --> 01:09:08.812
Na pensheni yako.

01:09:18.123 --> 01:09:19.361
Punda.

01:09:51.158 --> 01:09:52.592
Jonathan Wick?

01:10:10.012 --> 01:10:11.442
Unasahau

01:10:11.442 --> 01:10:14.446
sisi bado
chini ya Jedwali.

01:10:14.446 --> 01:10:17.149
Na mwisho niliangalia ...

01:10:17.149 --> 01:10:19.350
... wewe ni Excommunicado

01:10:19.350 --> 01:10:22.556
na tikiti yako
ilichanika.

01:10:23.788 --> 01:10:27.297
Huna biashara
pamoja nasi.

01:10:30.130 --> 01:10:31.763
Pyotr amekufa!

01:10:36.675 --> 01:10:38.305
Baada yako

01:10:38.305 --> 01:10:40.508
weka risasi
katika kichwa cha Mzee,

01:10:42.347 --> 01:10:44.842
Marquis alikuwa na moja
kuweka katika Pyotr's.

01:10:45.943 --> 01:10:49.350
Na katika faini
Tamaduni ya Kirusi ...

01:10:49.350 --> 01:10:52.047
Alitutumia bili.

01:10:53.792 --> 01:10:55.351
Kwa sababu yako,

01:10:55.351 --> 01:10:56.820
Ilibidi nipige magoti

01:10:56.820 --> 01:10:59.755
mbele ya mwanaume huyo
aliyemuua baba yangu.

01:10:59.755 --> 01:11:01.995
Kisha tuna

01:11:01.995 --> 01:11:03.663
adui wa pamoja.

01:11:05.035 --> 01:11:07.932
Tunaweza kusaidiana.

01:11:07.932 --> 01:11:12.134
Hata huwezi
jisaidie.

01:11:12.134 --> 01:11:14.569
Jinsi kuzimu
unakwenda
kutusaidia?

01:11:14.569 --> 01:11:18.475
Kwa kuua Marquis hii.

01:11:18.475 --> 01:11:20.376
Wao tu
kuteua mwingine.

01:11:24.889 --> 01:11:26.482
Inafanya

01:11:26.482 --> 01:11:29.491
ikiwa nitamuua kwenye duwa!

01:12:10.499 --> 01:12:12.395
Umeua wangapi

01:12:12.395 --> 01:12:13.562
kupata nje?

01:12:13.562 --> 01:12:15.702
Mengi.

01:12:16.802 --> 01:12:18.837
Utakuwa nayo tu
kuua mmoja

01:12:19.405 --> 01:12:20.706
kurejea ndani.

01:12:20.706 --> 01:12:23.809
Mwanaharamu ambaye
alimuua baba yangu.

01:12:25.412 --> 01:12:27.978
Nipe jina.

01:12:29.184 --> 01:12:30.880
Killa Harkan.

01:12:30.880 --> 01:12:33.487
Utampata
katika Himmel na Hölle.

01:12:33.487 --> 01:12:36.324
Wakati amekufa,
Nitarekebisha tikiti yako.

01:12:36.324 --> 01:12:38.654
Na Crest?

01:12:38.654 --> 01:12:41.563
Harkan kwanza, kisha tunazungumza.

01:12:42.231 --> 01:12:43.930
Lete uthibitisho wa kifo.

01:12:47.038 --> 01:12:48.867
Nitahitaji njia ya kuingia.

01:12:51.473 --> 01:12:53.069
Najua njia.

01:12:54.209 --> 01:12:55.511
Klaus atakuchukua.

01:13:04.823 --> 01:13:06.115
Mimi ni Klaus.

01:13:10.788 --> 01:13:12.856
Yohana.
Mimi ni Klaus.

01:14:01.608 --> 01:14:02.873
Tafadhali mwambie bibi yako

01:14:02.873 --> 01:14:04.845
kwamba ninaheshimiwa
kwa ishara hii

01:14:04.845 --> 01:14:07.847
na ninatazamia
ushirikiano wetu unaoendelea.

01:14:09.251 --> 01:14:10.553
Mimi ni Klaus.

01:14:17.523 --> 01:14:20.057
Bw. John Wick

01:14:20.658 --> 01:14:22.129
katika mwili.

01:14:23.659 --> 01:14:26.965
Baba Yaga.

01:14:28.206 --> 01:14:29.497
Lazima Krismasi, <i>je?</i>

01:14:40.812 --> 01:14:42.717
Wako wapi
adabu zangu? Tafadhali.

01:14:48.654 --> 01:14:50.791
Kinywaji, Bw. Wick?

01:14:53.991 --> 01:14:55.996
Ulikuwa
kunitarajia.

01:14:55.996 --> 01:14:57.160
Si mimi.

01:14:58.331 --> 01:14:59.536
Yeye.

01:15:00.334 --> 01:15:01.399
Yohana?

01:15:04.108 --> 01:15:05.102
Habari yako?

01:15:07.145 --> 01:15:09.077
Ulijua nitakuwa hapa.

01:15:09.077 --> 01:15:10.844
Nilishuku.

01:15:11.542 --> 01:15:12.780
Familia.

01:15:17.555 --> 01:15:20.722
Familia hiyo
kuuzwa wewe nje, Bw. Wick.

01:15:22.390 --> 01:15:23.724
Walikutoa

01:15:23.724 --> 01:15:26.189
kwa matumaini bure
ya kujiokoa.

01:15:27.458 --> 01:15:29.660
Unaona, ndiyo sababu
Siamini kamwe Cossacks.

01:15:29.660 --> 01:15:32.397
Ni watu wachafu.

01:15:35.701 --> 01:15:37.772
Hii ni ya kibinafsi.

01:15:40.277 --> 01:15:41.974
Nahisi mvutano hapa.

01:15:43.547 --> 01:15:45.845
Bw. Wick anaweza
pengine kujisikia

01:15:45.845 --> 01:15:48.585
Ninawajibika
kwa kifo cha...

01:15:49.516 --> 01:15:50.818
rafiki wa pande zote.

01:15:54.085 --> 01:15:57.154
Lakini sikumuua Koji.
Ulifanya, John.

01:15:59.491 --> 01:16:02.361
Unajua,
mfarakano huu
kati ya marafiki wa zamani,

01:16:02.361 --> 01:16:03.798
inanisikitisha.

01:16:05.203 --> 01:16:06.196
Niruhusu nisaidie.

01:16:09.106 --> 01:16:10.134
<i>Nein.</i>

01:16:11.538 --> 01:16:12.774
Tuna mpango.

01:16:15.540 --> 01:16:16.738
Alikuwa.

01:16:16.738 --> 01:16:18.274
Marquis.

01:16:18.274 --> 01:16:20.414
Kuzimu, nina shaka ataweza
Akili ikiwa ni risasi,

01:16:20.414 --> 01:16:22.248
visu au kipofu.

01:16:43.071 --> 01:16:45.873
Je!
kwa ajili yangu, Bw...

01:16:47.176 --> 01:16:48.172
Hakuna mtu.

01:16:49.943 --> 01:16:52.143
Na, hapana, ni kweli
kwa ajili yake.

01:16:56.985 --> 01:17:00.120
Kisha kuchukua
kiti,
Bwana Hakuna.

01:17:04.055 --> 01:17:05.860
Inasisimua, <i>je?</i>

01:17:15.604 --> 01:17:18.972
Kwa hiyo, unataka kumuua.

01:17:21.642 --> 01:17:22.943
Unataka kumuua.

01:17:24.315 --> 01:17:25.847
Nataka kumuua.

01:17:26.946 --> 01:17:28.751
Vipi kuhusu
wewe, Bw. Wick?

01:17:29.419 --> 01:17:31.419
Nitakuua.

01:17:31.419 --> 01:17:32.751
Oh.

01:17:32.751 --> 01:17:35.219
Kwa Pyotr. Bila shaka, <i>ja.</i>

01:17:36.761 --> 01:17:39.725
Lakini inaonekana kama
tuna wenyewe, uh,

01:17:39.725 --> 01:17:42.698
kitendawili cha kweli.

01:17:42.698 --> 01:17:46.201
Shida, ikiwa unataka.
Shida ya maisha halisi.

01:17:47.863 --> 01:17:49.200
Hivyo...

01:17:50.837 --> 01:17:53.142
Vipi kuhusu sisi kucheza mchezo?

01:17:53.142 --> 01:17:54.271
Mkono mmoja.

01:17:55.139 --> 01:17:57.307
Mshindi ndiye anaamua nani anaishi...

01:17:59.350 --> 01:18:00.810
na ambaye hana.

01:18:05.820 --> 01:18:08.852
Sawa.
Je, kununua ni nini?

01:18:08.852 --> 01:18:11.154
Zaidi ya unaweza kumudu.

01:18:11.154 --> 01:18:13.022
Ndiyo,
Niko mbali na risasi moja

01:18:13.022 --> 01:18:15.226
kutokana na kuwa mtu tajiri sana.

01:18:16.762 --> 01:18:18.130
Au aliyekufa.

01:18:20.403 --> 01:18:23.168
Kuchora kwa kadi tano.

01:18:47.297 --> 01:18:48.325
Bwana Wick.

01:18:49.465 --> 01:18:50.767
Bw. Wick?

01:19:14.052 --> 01:19:16.155
Mkono wa mtu aliyekufa, Bw. Wick.

01:19:20.164 --> 01:19:21.160
Naam...

01:19:22.531 --> 01:19:24.130
sichezi kamari.

01:19:26.765 --> 01:19:27.969
Hebu tuone.

01:19:35.512 --> 01:19:37.777
Tisa nne. Na nne.

01:19:37.777 --> 01:19:40.278
Ya kuvutia zaidi.

01:19:52.122 --> 01:19:55.563
Ah. Kifalme flush.

01:19:55.563 --> 01:19:57.365
Nzuri sana kwa mtu yeyote.

01:19:57.365 --> 01:19:58.527
Asante.

01:20:00.572 --> 01:20:03.803
Kipofu,
kijana na mbwa

01:20:03.803 --> 01:20:05.838
na John Wick huingia kwenye baa

01:20:05.838 --> 01:20:09.306
na uketi mezani.

01:20:09.306 --> 01:20:11.446
Hiyo inasikika
kama mwanzo

01:20:11.446 --> 01:20:13.011
ya mzaha wa ajabu

01:20:13.011 --> 01:20:15.680
au zaidi
fursa ya faida.

01:20:17.820 --> 01:20:22.023
Mtu anadhani anaweza
kumtumikia njia yake ya kutoka.

01:20:26.429 --> 01:20:27.589
Moja...

01:20:28.864 --> 01:20:31.164
anadhani anaweza
kununua njia yake ya kutoka.

01:20:33.997 --> 01:20:35.432
Na moja...

01:20:36.936 --> 01:20:38.402
anadhani anaweza kuua

01:20:39.476 --> 01:20:40.602
njia yake ya kutoka.

01:20:43.347 --> 01:20:46.542
Kila mmoja wao anafikiria
waliyo nayo
mkono wa kushinda.

01:20:47.947 --> 01:20:49.281
Lakini wanashindwa nini

01:20:50.321 --> 01:20:51.779
kutambua

01:20:51.779 --> 01:20:55.518
ndio muda waliouchukua
kiti kwenye Meza...

01:20:58.892 --> 01:21:00.860
tayari walikuwa wamepoteza.

01:21:00.860 --> 01:21:03.361
Acha nifikirie.
Tano za aina?

01:21:04.997 --> 01:21:06.093
Ndiyo.

01:21:13.544 --> 01:21:15.043
Ili tu ujue,

01:21:16.305 --> 01:21:18.376
Pyotr hakuwa mtu binafsi.

01:21:20.177 --> 01:21:21.379
Sasa, labda kidogo.

01:21:24.982 --> 01:21:27.822
Kuua!

01:22:46.530 --> 01:22:48.466
Habari!
Yuko pale!

01:25:43.606 --> 01:25:45.709
Karanga!

01:26:14.277 --> 01:26:16.443
Jua nini
shida yako ni,
Bw. Wick?

01:26:17.077 --> 01:26:19.512
Huna bahati.

01:26:20.982 --> 01:26:22.482
Bahati mbaya maishani,

01:26:22.982 --> 01:26:24.345
katika mapenzi,

01:26:24.345 --> 01:26:26.222
katika urafiki...

01:26:28.417 --> 01:26:29.687
na sasa...

01:26:31.222 --> 01:26:32.692
katika kifo.

01:27:32.187 --> 01:27:34.422
Killa!

01:28:23.270 --> 01:28:25.968
Kwa nini usifanye hivyo
kufa tu?

01:29:33.603 --> 01:29:34.839
Yeye ni wangu.

01:29:36.939 --> 01:29:38.978
Nilikuambia
sio kuchukua dili.

01:29:38.978 --> 01:29:41.417
Ndio, nadhani
mpango wako haukufaulu
fanya kazi ama, huh?

01:29:42.181 --> 01:29:44.016
Huh?

01:29:44.016 --> 01:29:46.554
Kuzimu ya kitu
ili wachukue
macho yako, ingawa.

01:29:51.226 --> 01:29:52.461
Hawakuzichukua.

01:29:54.624 --> 01:29:55.827
Niliwapa.

01:31:32.124 --> 01:31:34.556
Warumi wa Urusi
itaunga mkono

01:31:34.556 --> 01:31:35.828
changamoto yako.

01:31:37.059 --> 01:31:38.633
Nani atakuwa
yako ya Pili?

01:32:07.124 --> 01:32:09.961
Onyo
ya gharama ya udhalimu.

01:32:13.395 --> 01:32:16.731
Lazima nia
kujiunga na concierge yako.

01:32:16.731 --> 01:32:18.068
Sio leo.

01:32:25.207 --> 01:32:27.314
Kwa Njia za Zamani
na sheria za zamani,

01:32:27.314 --> 01:32:30.113
John Wick anakuita kwenye duwa.

01:32:30.113 --> 01:32:32.747
Ili kutatua tofauti zenu
njia ya kizamani,

01:32:32.747 --> 01:32:34.755
kama waungwana wanapaswa.

01:32:36.991 --> 01:32:39.353
Unazungumza juu ya Njia za Kale
kana kwamba unawajua.

01:32:40.530 --> 01:32:42.596
Mtu wa Bw. Wick's
kituo

01:32:42.596 --> 01:32:44.358
haiwezi kutoa
changamoto kama hiyo.

01:32:45.995 --> 01:32:48.131
Amewahi
kiumbe cha familia yake.

01:32:50.800 --> 01:32:52.135
Hmm.

01:32:53.108 --> 01:32:54.142
Berlin.

01:32:54.142 --> 01:32:55.602
Changamoto ya Ruska Roma,

01:32:55.602 --> 01:32:57.606
kukubalika
ya Bw. Wick
kurudi kwenye zizi,

01:32:57.606 --> 01:32:59.345
yote yapo.

01:32:59.345 --> 01:33:01.078
Historia iliyorekodiwa sasa.

01:33:09.624 --> 01:33:11.324
Na kwa nini mimi
ukubali hii

01:33:11.324 --> 01:33:12.960
kutoka kwa kiti cha daraja la pili?

01:33:12.960 --> 01:33:15.289
Kwa sababu huko
ni kanuni,
na bila wao ...

01:33:15.289 --> 01:33:18.326
Tunaishi na
wanyama. Hasa.

01:33:19.796 --> 01:33:20.999
Mm.

01:33:21.898 --> 01:33:23.364
Nyakati zinabadilika.

01:33:24.274 --> 01:33:25.702
Siku mpya inapambazuka.

01:33:25.702 --> 01:33:28.644
Mawazo mapya, sheria mpya,

01:33:29.509 --> 01:33:30.877
usimamizi mpya.

01:33:32.942 --> 01:33:35.077
Hata hivyo utakubali.

01:33:35.077 --> 01:33:39.084
Kwa sababu sisi sote bado tunakaa
chini ya Jedwali.

01:33:39.084 --> 01:33:42.383
Hata wewe huna kinga
kwa matokeo ya kushindwa.

01:33:50.261 --> 01:33:53.328
Na nini hasa
ni masharti ya Bw. Wick?

01:33:54.171 --> 01:33:56.731
<i>Victoriae fiducia.</i>

01:33:56.731 --> 01:34:01.710
Kutolewa bila masharti
wa wajibu wowote na wote
kwa Jedwali.

01:34:16.054 --> 01:34:18.959
Ah, historia imejaa
akiwa na Marquis

01:34:18.959 --> 01:34:21.389
ambao walikuwa
kukumbukwa tu
na watumishi wao.

01:34:22.198 --> 01:34:23.259
Lakini wewe...

01:34:25.161 --> 01:34:26.601
unaweza
kukumbukwa

01:34:26.601 --> 01:34:29.030
kama mtu aliyeleta
John Wick,

01:34:29.030 --> 01:34:30.764
zaidi
kuogopwa na wote

01:34:30.764 --> 01:34:33.368
na Jedwali
na wote wanaoketi humo,
kwenye mwanga.

01:34:34.838 --> 01:34:36.206
Nuru yako.

01:34:38.447 --> 01:34:39.943
Na ni nani angeweza kutabiri

01:34:39.943 --> 01:34:42.043
jinsi ya juu
utukufu wa namna hiyo

01:34:42.043 --> 01:34:44.445
inaweza kuchukua mwanaume
katika ulimwengu wetu?

01:35:01.333 --> 01:35:05.070
Mchana, <i>La Tour Eiffel,</i>
kujadili kanuni.

01:35:05.935 --> 01:35:07.204
Unaweza kwenda.

01:35:08.377 --> 01:35:09.437
Nikimaliza.

01:35:10.879 --> 01:35:12.542
Kama yake ya Pili,
juu ya ushindi wake,

01:35:12.542 --> 01:35:16.278
Excommunicado yangu
ni kuinuliwa,
jina langu limerejeshwa,

01:35:16.278 --> 01:35:19.279
hoteli yangu imejengwa upya
na kuwekwa wakfu tena,

01:35:19.279 --> 01:35:21.350
yote kwa
Gharama ya Jedwali.

01:35:23.688 --> 01:35:24.892
Bila shaka.

01:35:35.135 --> 01:35:37.839
Jinsi unavyofanya chochote
ndivyo unavyofanya kila kitu.

01:35:39.771 --> 01:35:40.974
Sasa nimemaliza.

01:35:45.079 --> 01:35:47.009
Nadhani nitakukosa
wakati umekwenda.

01:35:47.009 --> 01:35:49.081
Aibu siwezi
sema sawa.

01:35:49.981 --> 01:35:51.512
Hujui,
wewe je?

01:35:52.619 --> 01:35:54.821
Ni nini hicho?

01:35:54.821 --> 01:35:57.989
Pili ya Mwanaume,
kama mfadhili wake,

01:35:57.989 --> 01:36:00.086
ama anatoka nje
akiwa na bingwa wake

01:36:00.086 --> 01:36:02.061
au amezikwa kando yake.

01:36:03.630 --> 01:36:05.163
Njia za Zamani.

01:36:13.409 --> 01:36:14.469
Ndivyo maisha.

01:37:01.823 --> 01:37:03.986
Chini ya Sheria za Kale,

01:37:03.986 --> 01:37:06.253
mmoja tu anaweza kuishi.

01:37:06.253 --> 01:37:08.061
Je, ninyi wawili
kuelewa hilo?

01:37:11.798 --> 01:37:13.234
Nzuri sana.

01:37:13.234 --> 01:37:15.099
Kanuni.

01:37:15.099 --> 01:37:18.005
Wenye Changamoto
huchagua kwanza. Wakati?

01:37:19.836 --> 01:37:21.107
Kuchomoza kwa jua.

01:37:26.744 --> 01:37:27.982
Sasa.

01:37:31.752 --> 01:37:33.086
Kuchomoza kwa jua.

01:37:33.587 --> 01:37:34.582
Mahali?

01:37:35.722 --> 01:37:37.488
Njoo hapa

01:37:37.488 --> 01:37:40.027
kufikiri kuna
njia ya kutoka katika ulimwengu huu
kwa ajili yako, Bw. Wick?

01:37:42.058 --> 01:37:43.327
Hakuna.

01:37:46.195 --> 01:37:48.068
Kituo cha Pompidou.

01:37:50.770 --> 01:37:52.369
Sacré Coeur.

01:37:57.073 --> 01:37:58.342
Sacré Coeur.

01:37:59.546 --> 01:38:00.542
Silaha?

01:38:01.616 --> 01:38:02.981
Ukishinda,

01:38:02.981 --> 01:38:05.052
Jedwali mapenzi
heshimu neno lake.

01:38:06.152 --> 01:38:07.516
Utakuwa na
uhuru wako.

01:38:08.921 --> 01:38:10.354
Lakini hautachukua.

01:38:11.624 --> 01:38:12.620
Blades.

01:38:18.598 --> 01:38:19.935
Bastola.

01:38:24.668 --> 01:38:29.043
Dueling bastola.
Hatua thelathini.

01:38:29.043 --> 01:38:31.509
Katika tukio hilo
pande zote mbili kuishi,

01:38:31.509 --> 01:38:34.977
kila mmoja atamkaribia mwenzake
kwa nyongeza za hatua kumi

01:38:34.977 --> 01:38:37.414
mpaka kubaki mmoja tu.

01:38:38.852 --> 01:38:40.252
Kanuni za ushiriki.

01:38:41.524 --> 01:38:42.983
Hakuna robo.

01:38:42.983 --> 01:38:45.620
Unajua kwa nini
hautachukua
uhuru wako?

01:38:46.494 --> 01:38:47.523
Hmm?

01:38:49.029 --> 01:38:51.131
Kwa sababu hii
wewe ni nani,

01:38:52.032 --> 01:38:53.562
una nani
daima imekuwa.

01:38:55.836 --> 01:38:57.665
Wewe ni muuaji.

01:39:00.010 --> 01:39:02.642
Yatima tulimchuna
kutoka mitaani

01:39:02.642 --> 01:39:05.177
na kupamba kisu.

01:39:05.177 --> 01:39:08.082
Na ni mauaji
hiyo inakupa kusudi.

01:39:09.082 --> 01:39:11.019
Mwanaume
bila kusudi...

01:39:12.819 --> 01:39:14.154
si kitu.

01:39:16.559 --> 01:39:17.751
Hakuna robo.

01:39:19.387 --> 01:39:21.259
Hakuna robo.

01:39:21.259 --> 01:39:24.194
Ikiwa hakuna kitu kingine, waheshimiwa,

01:39:24.194 --> 01:39:26.001
nitaona...
Uteuzi.

01:39:30.474 --> 01:39:31.567
Ni haki yake.

01:39:33.338 --> 01:39:35.010
Je, una jina?

01:39:40.010 --> 01:39:41.247
Kaini.

01:39:43.785 --> 01:39:45.620
Na iwe hivyo.

01:39:45.620 --> 01:39:47.583
Macheo, Sacré Coeur.

01:39:49.188 --> 01:39:51.551
Bastola za risasi,
hakuna robo.

01:39:51.551 --> 01:39:54.095
Je, Bw. Wick
kuwa mshindi,

01:39:54.095 --> 01:39:55.992
atakuwa huru kwa lolote
na wajibu wote

01:39:55.992 --> 01:39:57.657
kwa Meza ya Juu,

01:39:57.657 --> 01:39:59.999
na ya Pili yake
itarejeshwa

01:39:59.999 --> 01:40:02.296
kama meneja
ya kujengwa upya

01:40:02.296 --> 01:40:04.072
New York Continental.

01:40:05.773 --> 01:40:09.808
Je, Marquis
Vincent Bisset de Gramont
kuwa mshindi...

01:40:09.808 --> 01:40:11.574
John Wick atakuwa amekufa.

01:40:13.848 --> 01:40:15.380
Kama ya Pili yake.

01:40:17.247 --> 01:40:19.019
Hivyo tu.

01:40:19.019 --> 01:40:20.415
Sasa, kama ipo
hakuna zaidi waheshimiwa,

01:40:20.415 --> 01:40:22.650
nitakuona
jua linapochomoza.

01:40:22.650 --> 01:40:24.452
Kukosa kukutana
kwa saa iliyopangwa

01:40:24.452 --> 01:40:26.055
itasababisha
katika kunyang'anywa

01:40:26.055 --> 01:40:28.294
na utekelezaji wa haraka.

01:40:39.270 --> 01:40:42.341
Hakuna Yohana
huko nje.

01:40:43.575 --> 01:40:46.345
Hakuna mume mwenye furaha
na maisha ya kawaida.

01:40:49.147 --> 01:40:50.580
Kuna John Wick tu,

01:40:51.555 --> 01:40:52.648
muuaji.

01:40:54.990 --> 01:40:57.125
Na atakuua.

01:41:03.799 --> 01:41:04.858
<i>Hoteli yako?</i>

01:41:05.963 --> 01:41:07.266
Ndiyo.

01:41:07.266 --> 01:41:09.262
Una kila wakati
pembeni, sivyo?

01:41:09.262 --> 01:41:11.269
Je, si kila mtu?

01:41:11.269 --> 01:41:15.142
Tutafute bandari salama
kabla haijaanza.

01:41:15.142 --> 01:41:17.074
Kuna kitu
Nahitaji kufanya kwanza.

01:41:17.074 --> 01:41:19.543
Mapema afadhali
kuliko baadaye.

01:41:23.246 --> 01:41:24.917
Sitafanya hivyo.

01:41:24.917 --> 01:41:26.451
Unapigana
vita yako mwenyewe.

01:41:30.355 --> 01:41:32.193
Si hii
unataka nini?

01:41:33.925 --> 01:41:35.389
Hmm?

01:41:35.389 --> 01:41:37.198
<i>Victoriae fiducia.</i>

01:41:38.228 --> 01:41:39.562
Unamuua,

01:41:39.562 --> 01:41:41.598
na wewe na yako
binti atakuwa huru.

01:41:43.773 --> 01:41:45.272
Hakuna anayeweza kumgusa.

01:41:46.775 --> 01:41:48.605
Ikiwa hutafanya hivyo,

01:41:48.605 --> 01:41:51.443
itabidi akabiliane nayo
matokeo.

01:41:53.013 --> 01:41:55.150
Chaguo ni lako.

01:43:21.704 --> 01:43:22.765
Kaini.

01:43:23.706 --> 01:43:24.833
Yohana.

01:43:25.973 --> 01:43:27.341
Kusema kwaheri?

01:43:29.273 --> 01:43:30.905
Kusema hello.

01:43:36.185 --> 01:43:37.978
Unafikiri mke wako
unaweza kusikia wewe?

01:43:40.590 --> 01:43:41.685
Hapana.

01:43:45.256 --> 01:43:46.591
Basi kwa nini kujisumbua?

01:43:48.732 --> 01:43:50.265
Labda nina makosa.

01:43:54.001 --> 01:43:55.600
Wafu wametoweka.

01:43:59.172 --> 01:44:00.968
Jambo lililo hai tu.

01:44:06.412 --> 01:44:08.712
Baada ya binti yangu kuzaliwa...

01:44:10.614 --> 01:44:12.281
Nilitaka kuacha maisha haya.

01:44:14.854 --> 01:44:16.291
Nilidhani nilifanya.

01:44:18.520 --> 01:44:20.020
Lakini hukufanya.

01:44:22.293 --> 01:44:23.727
Tumelaaniwa...

01:44:25.900 --> 01:44:26.994
wewe na mimi.

01:44:28.465 --> 01:44:30.569
Juu ya hilo tunakubaliana.

01:44:34.636 --> 01:44:36.443
Binti yangu sio.

01:44:39.610 --> 01:44:41.679
Ikiwa ni kati
wewe na yeye...

01:44:43.853 --> 01:44:45.485
utakufa.

01:44:52.289 --> 01:44:53.856
Labda sivyo.

01:44:59.067 --> 01:45:00.599
Nilikukosa, John.

01:45:02.668 --> 01:45:05.472
Ni nzuri sana
kukaa na rafiki.

01:45:10.441 --> 01:45:12.545
Nitakuona kesho.

01:45:42.608 --> 01:45:45.476
Hivi ndivyo wewe
kutatua hali hiyo?

01:45:45.476 --> 01:45:47.680
Duello na
Baba Yaga.

01:45:47.680 --> 01:45:50.913
Kushindwa kutatikisa
msingi
wa Meza ya Juu,

01:45:52.321 --> 01:45:55.555
na itageuka Wick
ndani ya mtakatifu.

01:45:58.227 --> 01:46:00.553
Ushindi wangu utakuwa
fanya kinyume chake.

01:46:03.130 --> 01:46:04.729
Marquis de Gramont!

01:46:06.397 --> 01:46:08.563
Tamaa ya mtu

01:46:08.563 --> 01:46:10.900
kamwe isizidi thamani yake.

01:46:13.772 --> 01:46:16.807
Ungefanya vyema
kukumbuka hilo, bwana.

01:47:37.557 --> 01:47:39.558
<i>Bonjour,</i>
Monsieur Wick.

01:47:39.558 --> 01:47:42.494
Na kuwakaribisha
kwa <i>La Upinzani.</i>

01:47:42.494 --> 01:47:44.658
Mbali kidogo na nyumbani,
si wewe?

01:47:44.658 --> 01:47:46.092
Kweli, kitendo chako kidogo

01:47:46.092 --> 01:47:48.728
ya uasi usio wa kiungwana
ilinitia moyo, John.

01:47:48.728 --> 01:47:50.400
Mimi natoka nje,

01:47:50.400 --> 01:47:52.703
kueneza mbawa zangu.

01:47:52.703 --> 01:47:54.773
Mkuu unaendeleaje
Ziara ya Kuaga?

01:47:56.442 --> 01:47:57.974
Kufika mwisho.

01:47:58.906 --> 01:48:01.241
Hivyo inaonekana. Hivyo inaonekana.

01:48:02.418 --> 01:48:04.519
Arobaini na mbili za kawaida,
sivyo?

01:48:05.520 --> 01:48:07.046
Ni Kevlar,
mbele kwa nyuma.

01:48:07.046 --> 01:48:08.983
Ya hivi punde
katika chic ballistiska.

01:48:08.983 --> 01:48:10.854
Inafaa kwa
hafla zote rasmi.

01:48:10.854 --> 01:48:14.055
Harusi, mazishi,
Mapigano ya Jedwali la Juu.

01:48:14.055 --> 01:48:15.791
Baada ya yote, mwanaume
inabidi aonekane bora

01:48:15.791 --> 01:48:17.631
wakati umefika
kuolewa.

01:48:19.166 --> 01:48:20.161
Au kuzikwa.

01:48:31.014 --> 01:48:32.074
Nisamehe bwana,

01:48:32.841 --> 01:48:34.307
lakini huu ni wazimu.

01:48:35.511 --> 01:48:36.978
Wazimu?

01:48:36.978 --> 01:48:39.015
Kuamini hatima yako
kwa kipofu?

01:48:40.315 --> 01:48:43.184
Kuna aina tatu
ya wanaume katika dunia hii.

01:48:44.958 --> 01:48:48.024
Wale ambao
kuwa na kitu
kuishi kwa,

01:48:48.024 --> 01:48:51.127
wale ambao
kuwa na kitu
kufa kwa ajili ya,

01:48:51.127 --> 01:48:53.994
na wale ambao
kuwa na kitu
kuua kwa.

01:48:53.994 --> 01:48:56.735
John Wick ana
hakuna mambo haya.

01:48:56.735 --> 01:49:00.036
Yeye ni mzimu tu
katika kutafuta makaburi.

01:49:01.473 --> 01:49:02.874
Lakini yule kipofu,

01:49:04.180 --> 01:49:05.679
vizuri, ana zote tatu.

01:49:07.414 --> 01:49:09.447
Isitoshe, nina hisia

01:49:09.447 --> 01:49:11.646
Bw. Wick hatafanikiwa kamwe

01:49:11.646 --> 01:49:13.819
kwa duwa na jua.

01:49:58.662 --> 01:50:00.230
Vema, sasa.

01:50:00.230 --> 01:50:03.035
Kwa nyinyi nyote huko nje
katika Jiji la Taa,

01:50:03.035 --> 01:50:07.000
kwa watu wote wa mitaani
kwa sikio kwa kitendo,

01:50:07.000 --> 01:50:09.341
<i>kwa wasikilizaji wangu wote waaminifu</i>

01:50:09.341 --> 01:50:12.343
<i>wanaojua beat
wa mtaani...</i>

01:50:12.343 --> 01:50:16.981
<i>... usiku wa leo ni nafasi yako
kufanya muziki mzuri.</i>

01:50:16.981 --> 01:50:20.518
Nimeulizwa
kuwasilisha ombi maalum

01:50:20.518 --> 01:50:22.349
<i>kutoka kwa mpenzi wa siri.</i>

01:50:23.425 --> 01:50:25.055
<i>Inaonekana kuna mwiba</i>

01:50:25.055 --> 01:50:28.593
<i>katika mdogo wetu
kipande cha paradiso.</i>

01:50:28.593 --> 01:50:30.864
<i>Mtu mwovu kutoka kwa Tufaa Kubwa</i>

01:50:30.864 --> 01:50:34.295
<i>inatengeneza sauti
kwa mioyo yetu mitakatifu.</i>

01:50:35.471 --> 01:50:36.902
<i>Tunatoa wito</i>

01:50:36.902 --> 01:50:40.841
<i>kutoa midundo yako ngumu zaidi
kwa mtu huyu mweusi.</i>

01:50:40.841 --> 01:50:45.245
<i>Ikiwa unataka tuzo,
lazima umalize kabla ya jua kuchomoza.</i>

01:50:45.245 --> 01:50:47.413
Mzee huyu wa dhahabu,

01:50:47.413 --> 01:50:50.515
na ninamaanisha goli la dhahabu,

01:50:50.515 --> 01:50:53.215
huenda nje kwako, Bw. Wick.

01:50:55.118 --> 01:50:58.051
Na kumbuka,
hakuna pa kukimbilia.

01:52:03.856 --> 01:52:05.117
<i>Nataka kuwashukuru nyote</i>

01:52:05.117 --> 01:52:09.357
<i>kwa kusikiliza WUXIA,</i>

01:52:09.357 --> 01:52:12.597
<i>mahali kwa
burudani yako yote</i>

01:52:12.597 --> 01:52:14.799
<i>na mahitaji ya habari.</i>

01:52:14.799 --> 01:52:16.264
<i>Uwindaji mzuri.</i>

01:52:18.536 --> 01:52:20.203
Na hivyo huanza.

01:52:21.542 --> 01:52:23.844
Nitahitaji bunduki.

01:52:25.140 --> 01:52:26.814
Nilifikiri
hautawahi kuuliza.

01:52:28.142 --> 01:52:30.581
Viper ya Shimo la milimita tisa.

01:52:30.581 --> 01:52:32.347
Ulipataje hili?

01:52:32.347 --> 01:52:35.515
Najua mvulana
ambaye anajua mvulana
ambaye alimpiga risasi mtu.

01:52:36.659 --> 01:52:38.392
Raundi ya ishirini na moja
jarida la uwezo

01:52:38.392 --> 01:52:39.459
na fidia iliyojengwa

01:52:39.459 --> 01:52:41.361
kwa hakika hakuna muzzle flip.

01:52:41.361 --> 01:52:43.330
Mtazamo wa mbele wa fiber-optic,

01:52:43.330 --> 01:52:44.994
usalama mwingi,

01:52:44.994 --> 01:52:47.599
flared magwell
kwa upakiaji upya haraka,

01:52:47.599 --> 01:52:49.637
pauni mbili
kichocheo kikubwa,

01:52:49.637 --> 01:52:52.339
na kwa wale zaidi,
tutasemaje,

01:52:52.339 --> 01:52:54.103
mikutano ya karibu,

01:52:54.103 --> 01:52:57.240
huyu Viper anayo
fangs kali.

01:53:02.113 --> 01:53:05.083
Jinsi gani unaweza karibu
kunipeleka kanisani?

01:53:10.259 --> 01:53:11.320
Amina.

01:53:21.397 --> 01:53:24.069
Tuko hapa,
waungwana.

01:53:25.604 --> 01:53:26.703
Safari yako.

01:53:30.107 --> 01:53:31.512
Nilipokushauri

01:53:31.512 --> 01:53:32.940
sio kuzamisha
pinky wako

01:53:32.940 --> 01:53:34.780
kurudi kwenye bwawa hili,

01:53:34.780 --> 01:53:37.115
Sikufikiri
Ningelowa.

01:53:39.887 --> 01:53:42.153
Yote yatakwisha
baada ya leo.

01:53:45.088 --> 01:53:47.290
Nilipokuwa
kumzika Charon,

01:53:49.231 --> 01:53:52.262
Nilichanika
nini cha kuweka
kwenye kaburi lake.

01:53:53.528 --> 01:53:56.898
Maneno machache
kujumlisha
maisha yote?

01:53:56.898 --> 01:54:00.036
Uishi mfalme!

01:54:00.036 --> 01:54:02.107
Nilitengeneza yangu
miaka iliyopita.

01:54:03.476 --> 01:54:04.510
Kiasi.

01:54:04.510 --> 01:54:06.441
Kinabii.

01:54:07.615 --> 01:54:09.246
Uliamua nini?

01:54:10.252 --> 01:54:12.082
Rafiki.

01:54:12.082 --> 01:54:14.581
Hivyo ndivyo alivyokuwa
juu ya yote.

01:54:15.357 --> 01:54:16.484
Rafiki.

01:54:25.563 --> 01:54:28.199
<i>Au rudisha nyuma
et bonne chasse,
Monsieur</i> Wick.

01:54:29.933 --> 01:54:31.334
Asante, Mfalme.

01:54:33.903 --> 01:54:35.173
Yonathani.

01:54:36.311 --> 01:54:37.469
Winston.

01:54:37.469 --> 01:54:40.441
Macheo ni saa 6:03.

01:54:40.441 --> 01:54:43.181
Usichelewe
kwa ajili yetu sote, hmm?

01:54:52.726 --> 01:54:54.192
"Mume mpenzi."

01:54:54.626 --> 01:54:56.189
Hmm?

01:54:56.189 --> 01:54:58.564
Hiyo ndiyo ninayotaka kwangu.

01:54:58.564 --> 01:55:01.232
"John. Mpenzi mume."

01:55:31.026 --> 01:55:32.296
Imethibitishwa.

01:55:33.636 --> 01:55:35.502
<i>Habari njema, wapenzi.</i>

01:55:35.502 --> 01:55:37.169
Tuna muandamo.

01:55:38.303 --> 01:55:40.136
<i>Mtu wetu mweusi
imeonekana</i>

01:55:40.136 --> 01:55:42.472
<i>katika</i> Septième Arrondissement.

01:55:42.472 --> 01:55:46.475
<i>Nadhani ni wakati muafaka
tunampaka rangi nyekundu.</i>

01:57:48.997 --> 01:57:53.206
Inaonekana kama
marafiki zetu kwenye chama
akaangusha mpira,

01:57:53.206 --> 01:57:56.205
<i>na sasa inazunguka
kwa Arc de Triomphe.</i>

01:57:56.205 --> 01:57:58.211
<i>Wacha tuone ni nani atakayeichukua.</i>

02:00:03.001 --> 02:00:04.567
<i>Njooni sasa, watu.</i>

02:00:04.567 --> 02:00:06.735
Tutakuwa na
kufanya mengi zaidi.

02:00:10.640 --> 02:00:13.610
<i>Sasa, nani atakuwa
mshindi wetu mkubwa?</i>

02:02:41.325 --> 02:02:42.759
Huyu ni nani?

02:02:42.759 --> 02:02:44.392
Unajua, swali
unapaswa kuuliza,

02:02:44.392 --> 02:02:46.125
Duh, ni ngapi?

02:02:46.125 --> 02:02:48.532
Nadhani tuna
hali chini ya udhibiti.

02:02:57.343 --> 02:02:59.309
Kwa sababu njia
naona,

02:02:59.309 --> 02:03:02.141
<i>ni kwamba kama Bw. Johnny Boy
inaleta kanisa
kwa wakati,</i>

02:03:02.141 --> 02:03:04.847
hii inaweza kuwa yako
jana usiku kama Marquis.

02:04:17.985 --> 02:04:19.988
<i>Sasisho kidogo la trafiki.</i>

02:04:19.988 --> 02:04:23.630
<i>Ninawasikia wavulana kwa rangi nyeusi
haikuweza kuifanya.</i>

02:04:23.630 --> 02:04:26.532
<i>Rafiki yetu mbaya
iko kwenye harakati tena.</i>

02:04:26.532 --> 02:04:30.570
Anakuelekea,
wasikilizaji wangu wa tarehe 8.

02:06:34.226 --> 02:06:35.228
Ndiyo?

02:06:35.228 --> 02:06:37.691
Sawa. Una mpango.

02:06:37.691 --> 02:06:39.565
Sawa. 35 ndio.

02:06:39.565 --> 02:06:42.497
Hiyo haikuwa mpango wetu.

02:06:46.940 --> 02:06:49.207
Naam, hiyo ndiyo mpango pekee
inayotolewa leo.

02:07:12.763 --> 02:07:13.993
Mpate!

02:07:22.506 --> 02:07:23.608
Simu!

02:07:28.145 --> 02:07:30.281
Je!
Sasa, wewe
nisikilizeni.

02:07:30.281 --> 02:07:31.377
<i>Arobaini.</i>

02:07:32.815 --> 02:07:35.183
Unalipa kwa huduma.

02:07:47.864 --> 02:07:49.934
<i>Habari njema, wapenzi.</i>

02:07:52.165 --> 02:07:54.466
Bahati nasibu ilipanda tu.

02:12:54.001 --> 02:12:58.044
<i>Kwa nyinyi wote wapiga debe
bado umekaa pembeni,</i>

02:12:58.044 --> 02:13:01.443
<i>Bwana Wick ana
kanisa mbele.</i>

02:13:03.048 --> 02:13:05.818
<i>Tunakaribia kuishiwa na wakati.</i>

02:13:05.818 --> 02:13:07.852
<i>Nafasi ya mwisho ya kushinda tuzo</i>

02:13:07.852 --> 02:13:11.522
<i>kabla ya mapambazuko ya mwisho ya Bw. Wick.</i>

02:13:11.522 --> 02:13:16.260
<i>Kwa hivyo ni nani huko nje anaenda
kupanda hizo hatua 222?</i>

02:17:55.101 --> 02:17:58.377
Inaonekana Bw. Wick
hatajiunga nasi.

02:18:17.293 --> 02:18:18.562
Yohana?

02:18:21.263 --> 02:18:22.599
Yohana?

02:18:24.134 --> 02:18:25.563
Kaini.

02:18:25.563 --> 02:18:27.364
Jua linachomoza saa ngapi?

02:18:30.470 --> 02:18:31.707
Mbili...

02:18:33.013 --> 02:18:34.545
labda dakika tatu.

02:18:35.846 --> 02:18:39.077
Nakuhitaji ufike kileleni
ya ngazi hizo, John.

02:18:43.120 --> 02:18:44.390
Ndiyo.

02:18:51.491 --> 02:18:52.761
Tayari?

02:18:53.394 --> 02:18:54.730
Ndiyo.

02:19:13.514 --> 02:19:14.915
Kumi na mbili au tisa?

02:19:16.087 --> 02:19:17.115
Tisa.

02:19:50.586 --> 02:19:52.425
Sita juu. Asante.

02:21:07.697 --> 02:21:09.231
<i>Ciao, ciao,</i> Bwana Wick.

02:21:22.709 --> 02:21:24.011
Huwezi kunipiga risasi.

02:21:28.122 --> 02:21:29.720
Ndio, uko sawa.

02:21:30.519 --> 02:21:31.722
Lakini naweza kumpiga risasi.

02:21:44.000 --> 02:21:46.968
Lakini naweza kukupiga,
mama mzazi.

02:21:48.372 --> 02:21:49.641
Twende, John.

02:22:15.632 --> 02:22:17.629
Karanga.

02:22:25.377 --> 02:22:26.843
Ulimpiga puppy wangu.

02:22:43.991 --> 02:22:45.191
Unajua,
unanidai.

02:22:46.198 --> 02:22:47.193
Ndiyo.

02:22:55.871 --> 02:22:57.368
Hakuna cha kibinafsi, John.

02:22:58.508 --> 02:23:00.140
Tuko hata sasa.

02:23:01.181 --> 02:23:02.373
Ndiyo.

02:23:52.724 --> 02:23:54.799
Na kwa hivyo tunaanza.

02:24:15.122 --> 02:24:18.916
Tunatafuta ukweli
na itastahimili
matokeo.

02:24:18.916 --> 02:24:21.386
Matokeo.

02:24:41.006 --> 02:24:42.374
Endelea sasa. Njoo.

02:25:21.520 --> 02:25:22.920
Vyeo waungwana.

02:25:35.933 --> 02:25:38.397
Tuonane
katika maisha yajayo, ndugu.

02:25:40.538 --> 02:25:42.137
Hatua thelathini.

02:26:30.484 --> 02:26:32.891
Kumbuka
binti yako.
Furahi!

02:26:40.225 --> 02:26:43.132
Ni jua nzuri kama nini.

02:27:02.456 --> 02:27:04.483
Maneno ya mwisho, Winston?

02:27:05.855 --> 02:27:07.453
Burudika tu huko nje.

02:27:31.717 --> 02:27:33.578
Je, uko tayari, Bw. Caine?

02:27:40.327 --> 02:27:41.388
Bw. Wick?

02:28:06.080 --> 02:28:07.414
Moto!

02:28:27.705 --> 02:28:29.403
Hatua ishirini!

02:29:03.443 --> 02:29:04.471
Moto!

02:29:16.357 --> 02:29:17.352
Nzuri.

02:29:24.893 --> 02:29:26.691
Hatua kumi!

02:30:17.012 --> 02:30:18.446
Muue tu.

02:30:38.299 --> 02:30:40.501
Wale wanaong’ang’ania kifo,

02:30:42.102 --> 02:30:43.339
kuishi.

02:30:46.075 --> 02:30:48.278
Wale wanaong’ang’ania uzima,

02:30:49.482 --> 02:30:50.577
kufa.

02:31:00.791 --> 02:31:02.127
Moto!

02:31:41.063 --> 02:31:42.332
Kama mfadhili wako,

02:31:44.630 --> 02:31:46.600
Nadai <i>mapinduzi ya neema.</i>

02:31:50.373 --> 02:31:52.342
Silaha yako,
nipe.

02:31:53.176 --> 02:31:54.839
Ni binti yangu
bure sasa?

02:31:56.214 --> 02:31:58.447
<i>Oui.</i> Wewe
na binti yako.

02:31:59.113 --> 02:32:00.317
Furahia.

02:32:18.333 --> 02:32:19.864
Kanuni.
Ha.

02:32:21.601 --> 02:32:24.440
Mpumbavu wewe mwenye kiburi,

02:32:25.140 --> 02:32:26.706
hakupiga risasi.

02:32:27.912 --> 02:32:29.346
Matokeo.

02:32:45.424 --> 02:32:47.232
Hiyo ni nzuri jamani.

02:32:59.271 --> 02:33:00.608
Hmm.

02:33:07.416 --> 02:33:10.387
Wajibu wako
kwa Meza...

02:33:12.091 --> 02:33:14.252
ameridhika,
John Wick.

02:33:14.252 --> 02:33:15.524
Wewe ni huru.

02:33:20.628 --> 02:33:22.993
Kama wewe
na binti yako, bwana.

02:33:25.835 --> 02:33:28.801
Utakuwa
kurejeshwa kikamilifu,
Bwana Meneja.

02:33:30.107 --> 02:33:31.507
Masharti yako yote

02:33:32.846 --> 02:33:34.543
yatatimia.

02:33:40.386 --> 02:33:43.481
Biashara yetu hapa sasa
imehitimishwa.

02:33:43.481 --> 02:33:45.521
Siku njema.

02:34:26.261 --> 02:34:27.464
Ndugu yangu.

02:34:30.771 --> 02:34:32.364
Una deni langu moja.

02:34:35.005 --> 02:34:36.066
Ndiyo.

02:34:58.665 --> 02:34:59.793
Winston.

02:35:00.800 --> 02:35:01.993
Yonathani.

02:35:04.597 --> 02:35:06.470
Utanipeleka nyumbani?

02:35:13.439 --> 02:35:14.808
Bila shaka.

02:36:48.402 --> 02:36:49.672
Helen.

02:37:51.304 --> 02:37:53.571
Sikuwahi kufikiria
Ningeiona siku.

02:37:58.907 --> 02:38:01.876
Unafikiri yuko wapi,
mbinguni au kuzimu?

02:38:07.580 --> 02:38:08.949
Nani anajua?

02:39:05.373 --> 02:39:09.142
<i>♪ Umechukua kila kitu
Ninapenda kutoka kwangu ♪</i>

02:39:09.142 --> 02:39:11.712
<i>♪ Sasa ni wakati
Ili kulipa bei ♪</i>

02:39:11.712 --> 02:39:14.985
<i>♪ Naam, nitakuwa nikitembea bure ♪</i>

02:39:14.985 --> 02:39:19.716
<i>♪ nitairekebisha
Sitaomba msamaha ♪</i>

02:39:19.716 --> 02:39:24.257
<i>♪ Hakuna machozi kushoto kulia
Ninamwona Wick usiku wa leo ♪</i>

02:39:24.257 --> 02:39:28.932
<i>♪ Jicho kwa jicho
Maisha kwa ajili ya maisha ♪</i>

02:39:28.932 --> 02:39:33.563
<i>♪ nitakuona kuzimu
Kwa upande mwingine ♪</i>

02:39:33.563 --> 02:39:38.471
<i>♪ Jicho kwa jicho
Maisha kwa ajili ya maisha ♪</i>

02:39:38.471 --> 02:39:45.043
<i>♪ nitakuona kuzimu
Kwa upande mwingine, ♪</i>

02:39:45.043 --> 02:39:52.250
<i>♪ Nitajaribu kukuchomea ♪</i>

02:39:54.553 --> 02:40:01.964
<i>♪ nitakutana nawe
Katika maisha ya baadae ♪</i>

02:40:01.964 --> 02:40:07.267
<i>♪ Nitachukua jicho kwa jicho
Maisha kwa ajili ya maisha ♪</i>

02:40:07.267 --> 02:40:13.307
<i>♪ nitakuona kuzimu
Kwa upande mwingine ♪</i>

02:40:13.307 --> 02:40:17.774
<i>♪ Akupige magoti
Bora niombe niondoke ♪</i>

02:40:21.614 --> 02:40:26.889
<i>♪ nitakuona kuzimu
